[[Image:Scourge of Worlds cover.jpg|thumb|right|250 px|DVD Cover]] '''''A Scourge of Worlds: A Dungeons & Dragons Adventure''''' is an animated [[film]] or interactive adventure. In each scene, it allows the user a choice, and different endings or different paths to the same ending will be displayed depending upon that choice.
It was released by Rhino Theatrical in June of [[2003 in film|2003]].
It continued the tradition of '[[Choose Your Own Adventure]]' novels, using a D&D theme and storyline.
It was directed by Dan Krech.
